{"tid":1234300,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入唔住問問 其實個日103萬人上街 換左咩番黎？","createTime":"2019-06-17T01:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T02:40:21.000Z","uid":162765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e7586f4ce3b82d1143d5b88b31289d8b7f9795fe","tid":1234300,"uid":162765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:32:46.000Z","msg":"換左既係如期舉行會議 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />政府都當你係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實103萬上街 200萬零1個上街都好 只不過係數字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 200萬既民意 都係換左一句書面道歉 連拍條片 都懶 港仔呀 對一個直選政府 你唔係覺得個個星期日出黎行下 佢就撤回？取消暴動？不追究？審黑警？ 無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有問心個句 200萬人 實情有幾多個真心 出過黎 方便呃自己 ，滿足自己偽善心 ，叫你罷工罷課 真係會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人真係好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有心既係個日612出黎既人打到仆街既學生 而成個運動都因佢地個日出黎遊街示威衝擊 而得到關注<br />\n<br />\n最後 ，我懇求大家仔細諗諗 ，一個直選政府你行下街佢係唔會理你 ，最低限度你點都要諗下罷工掛 ，無多少付出 你想得到咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望各位認真諗下，方向其實你從來都有，大台個d指揮，我從來都未見到有成效，最怕你兄弟爬山，各有各玩，各有特色，最後一去不返。民氣永在，只要你係覺得呢件事係不公義。<br />\n<br />\n如果7婆再唔撤回惡法同暴動，我一定會閒日再走出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141d81f23a406080955f3324e3b6475a858d1a54","tid":1234300,"uid":162765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc091747d81ec0397f7d300eec8aadf9fe10a15e","tid":1234300,"uid":162765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi